	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Local meeting recorder + transcriber + note processor.

Keywords:
  rec         Toggle a stereo recording (mic = left/"Me", system audio = right/"Them"). Run again to stop.
  transcribe  Transcribe the newest recording (or a file you pass) into a speaker-labeled Markdown transcript.
  notes       Process the newest transcript: choose Minutes, Summary, Clean up, or type a Custom instruction.

First-time setup: run setup/install.sh (builds the Python venv) and follow setup/audio-setup.md (BlackHole + aggregate/multi-output devices). Requires Homebrew packages ffmpeg, switchaudio-osx, blackhole-2ch and a running Ollama. See README.md.</string>
